Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟这是一个由Facebook推出的明星框架，光环加身，似乎不可能失败\Nsucceed did a framework by Facebook was too big to fail but this isn't that kind
