Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.30,0:29:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始，熟悉Blot的工程师包括Shane，都表示说我们已经在Bolt上投入了太多，而且Bolt使用好好的\Ninitially a lot of the engineers that used bolt including Shane realized just what you said like look we've invested so much in this thing and it's it's really worked for all this stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.08,0:29:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,毫无疑问可以继续应对新的挑战\Ncertainly we can work through the next set of challenges we're having so
